org.eclipse.eef.properties.ui.internal.page

Class EEFTabbedPropertyViewer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.eef.properties.ui.internal.page.EEFTabbedPropertyViewer

  • public class EEFTabbedPropertyViewer
extends java.lang.Object
    Viewer representing the property sheet page. On the left side it contains a list of tabs and on the right side it contains the current selected tab.
